WEBVTT

00:00:02.507 --> 00:00:09.359
Well, good evening. Thank you for joining us to look at the Christmas lights; I thought that was kind of fun.

00:00:09.360 --> 00:00:19.839
Paisley's been asking—we drive by and she says, 'Daddy, I want to go look at the lights.'I said, 'Okay, let's go look at the lights.'So, I thought, why not bring you all with us?

00:00:19.840 --> 00:00:29.164
Hopefully, you had a little fun. I know it was kind of quick, but if you don't move quick, sometimes you've just got a little bit of time left walking around.

00:00:29.165 --> 00:00:42.799
Megan was ready to go, so I thought I'd bring y'all along. When you go to the Oklahoma City Zoo Lights, they're the best; it is phenomenal.

00:00:42.800 --> 00:00:52.217
They have a huge display at the Oklahoma City Zoo, and we'll go over there and look at the lights sometimes and drive through their park.

00:00:52.218 --> 00:01:01.839
They've closed off roads where you can see the animals; they're making noises as you're looking at the lights, and it's pretty cool.

00:01:01.840 --> 00:01:05.198
It's probably one of my top favorite things to do, but it's pretty expensive.

00:01:05.199 --> 00:01:18.758
I think it's about $60 to go, and it only lasts about an hour, so you burn that money pretty quick.

00:01:18.759 --> 00:01:27.676
The hot chocolate's expensive, too, but it's something fun to do every once in a while. That's what we did tonight. I thought we'd come on and pray.

00:01:27.677 --> 00:01:40.141
Diana and I have been listening to Joyce again, and she's been talking about pride and things the Lord shapes when you're on that potter's wheel and the Lord's telling you, 'I want you to study this.

00:01:40.142 --> 00:01:50.510
I want you to keep going. I want you to come deeper with Me.'As I keep telling you all, the Lord said that in 2026, He's drawing the bride closer to His side.

00:01:50.511 --> 00:02:02.232
There are great days of shakings and awakenings coming, and things the Lord is about to do with the body of Christ in 2026.

00:02:02.233 --> 00:02:18.985
2025 was for warning, but the manifestations of what He's told me are coming in 2026 will be a wake-up call—a wake-up call concerning the signs of the times of the coming of the Lord Jesus Christ.

00:02:18.986 --> 00:02:32.944
I say it over and over again. The Lord teaches me a lot about the love walk when people hurt or wound you, and you have to be quick to respond.

00:02:32.945 --> 00:02:36.625
I've said, 'Lord, what do you want me to do about this? How do you want me to handle this?

00:02:36.626 --> 00:02:43.069
I'm really ticked off.'And He says, 'Brandon, walk in love.

00:02:43.070 --> 00:02:48.277
Love never fails.'I say, 'They're wrong, Lord. This is wrong.

00:02:48.278 --> 00:02:54.605
I'm upset about this.'But love takes no account of a suffered wrong. Remember that.

00:02:54.606 --> 00:03:04.080
If you want to walk higher with the fire, you must learn to walk in love, even when people do you wrong.

00:03:04.081 --> 00:03:11.578
The first reaction is always where they're really at. Is it a quick repentance?

00:03:11.579 --> 00:03:18.591
Is it an excuse for how it happened? Is it 'I'm sorry,'or is it quick? That's why you can pinpoint people.

00:03:18.593 --> 00:03:26.958
But the Lord tells me that regardless of how people act or what they say, you are required to walk in love, for that's where the greater glory is.

00:03:26.959 --> 00:03:35.039
Remember what the angel said when he visited the other night?

00:03:35.040 --> 00:03:41.265
The angel with the opal armor. The glory of the Lord filled my home so strongly.

00:03:41.266 --> 00:03:53.835
It lasted for over a day after he visited. I've said before, 'I don't talk to angels,'but the angel had a word.

00:03:53.836 --> 00:04:02.190
He spoke: 'The Lord has sent me to give you a message. You want to know the key to the greater glory?

00:04:02.191 --> 00:04:16.907
You want to know how you're going to walk in the manifestations in these last days, how you'll be a frontrunner instead of the one tagging behind?'We say, 'Well, that's pride.'No, there are going to be trailblazers and there are going to be those following behind.

00:04:16.908 --> 00:04:26.932
I want to be walking with the King. When He's coming back and we're riding with Him, I want my horse to be on the front row.

00:04:26.933 --> 00:04:43.070
I want to hear Him say, 'Brandon, well done, son.'No matter how much people hurt or offend you, or how much they wound you in life—whether they are close to you or not—words hurt.

00:04:43.071 --> 00:04:48.180
People hurt people. It's not always intentional; sometimes people do it ignorantly.

00:04:48.181 --> 00:04:57.420
But I'm telling you, your first response must always be love. Sometimes you have to take a step back.

00:04:57.421 --> 00:05:03.726
In my own situations, I've noticed I sometimes freak out and say things.

00:05:03.727 --> 00:05:16.715
When I get wounded, I have a tendency to explode, and the Lord says, 'Draw back.'It's like a horse you pull back.

00:05:16.716 --> 00:05:28.497
What's your first reaction? Mine is usually anger, and I'll say a lot with my mouth, but the Lord says, 'Draw back. Love never fails, Brandon.

00:05:28.498 --> 00:05:45.175
Your job is to always walk in love.'When that angel visited and said, 'What is going to bring in the greater glory is a love foundation—your love walk.

00:05:45.176 --> 00:05:52.474
Where are you with your love?'It's the second time I've had angels talk to me like that.

00:05:52.475 --> 00:06:07.512
One was a couple of years ago on Valentine's Day. It was amazing.

00:06:07.513 --> 00:06:13.282
A lot of people say, 'I don't go with all that,'but it's still about love. Love never fails; God is love.

00:06:13.283 --> 00:06:24.251
The Lord said to me then that the thing he needs to know the most—what he'll be judged on the most—is: how did he treat his brethren?

00:06:24.252 --> 00:06:31.527
How did he walk in love? How do you walk in love toward your wife, your husband, and your kids?

00:06:31.528 --> 00:06:40.964
When people wound you, you don't have to allow them to keep hurting you, but your reaction to them is love.

00:06:40.965 --> 00:06:49.038
Now, trust is earned; I want you to understand that. It doesn't mean you trust everybody or let everyone into your circle.

00:06:49.039 --> 00:06:54.559
In fact, the first thing the Lord told me when I started this ministry was, 'Trust no one.

00:06:54.560 --> 00:07:07.204
Don't allow people in your inner circle, Brandon. There are things I will call you to do and say where you're not allowed to have friends. You'll be separated unto Me to say the hard things.

00:07:07.205 --> 00:07:28.159
There will be a target on you in the natural, and you will be required to take communion and fellowship with Me, and walk in love with your wife and kids.'I've learned even with family it's not always the easiest thing to do because they're not always going to 'get'you, and it's not required for them to get you.

00:07:28.160 --> 00:07:35.160
You are obedient unto God. The Lord even says to me regarding the emails we get, 'Fear God, not man.

00:07:35.161 --> 00:07:39.044
Fear Me, not man. Don't worry about what they're saying about you.

00:07:39.045 --> 00:07:43.305
Draw close to My side and walk with Me in this end-time harvest.

00:07:43.306 --> 00:07:54.239
Walk with Me and I'll use you greatly and mightily.'They won't understand why you're accelerating so quickly, but it's not for them.

00:07:54.240 --> 00:08:05.298
Keep humble. Keep your flesh under and keep the love walk straight.

00:08:05.299 --> 00:08:13.205
I had an opportunity this weekend to be really ticked off at some things.

00:08:13.206 --> 00:08:19.617
I'm telling you, I haven't been that mad in a long time, to the point where I was trembling.

00:08:19.618 --> 00:08:32.154
I asked, 'Lord, what do you want me to do about all this mess?'He said, "Walk in love."I said, "Are you telling me to walk in love? I'm going to go off.

00:08:32.155 --> 00:08:46.398
What do you want me to do, Lord?""Walk in love."I said, "Walk in love."The key to the greater glory, son, is even whenever you feel somebody has done you wrong—and they did—is to walk in love.

00:08:46.399 --> 00:08:51.289
Regardless of the excuses they try to make afterwards, wrong is wrong and right is right.

00:08:51.290 --> 00:08:59.074
It doesn't matter what their response is; your response is love. And that's what he said to me.

00:08:59.075 --> 00:09:05.622
And I said, "That's hard for my flesh to hear."I'm screaming inside, you know, and it's like that.

00:09:05.623 --> 00:09:13.472
Diana is upset. D is crying. And what do you do whenever you're wounded so deep by people that you love and trust?

00:09:13.473 --> 00:09:18.796
You walk in love. And that's why the Lord said, "It doesn't mean you have to keep planted there.

00:09:18.797 --> 00:09:23.377
It doesn't mean you have to keep doing these things. It's your choice.

00:09:23.378 --> 00:09:32.389
It's your choice if you want to walk in the greater glory. I will use you mightily. But God is love.

00:09:32.390 --> 00:09:42.956
It's not what he does; it's who he is."And if you want to walk by his side, even whenever it's something innocent or not innocent, it doesn't matter.

00:09:42.957 --> 00:09:52.026
I'm not looking at them; I'm looking at him. I'm staying vertical. And you must learn to stay vertical in these days ahead.

00:09:52.027 --> 00:09:59.838
The Lord showed me as I was walking even at Rhema tonight, he said, "You must learn to stay vertical.

00:09:59.839 --> 00:10:06.965
It's not always going to be easy because the devil wants you to go horizontal and look at everybody else and what they're doing."But what about them?

00:10:06.966 --> 00:10:15.317
How come them? And he said, "No, stay vertical. Who cares about what they're doing? Your job is to be the branch and stay on the vine.

00:10:15.318 --> 00:10:37.881
Your job is to keep looking at me."Because if you look at what's around you, your pride sets in and you start thinking, "Woe is me."You start singing a sad song, and everybody has a sad song they can sing about how people do you wrong or how people might have not done it intentionally or whatever.

00:10:37.882 --> 00:10:48.591
It doesn't matter. Your job is to always maintain love. Now, love doesn't mean you have to keep doing the same thing over and over again and allowing people to hurt you.

00:10:48.592 --> 00:11:01.728
The lesson is: don't allow people in your inner circle. I've learned a lot, and I'm trying to teach you all something because Brandon and I have learned a lot as we walk down the road.

00:11:01.729 --> 00:11:09.278
This has not been an easy journey for me, but I'm learning I want to walk with him.

00:11:09.279 --> 00:11:13.933
I always know when I've messed up because that anointing lifts off me.

00:11:13.934 --> 00:11:32.159
But he said, "Be angry and sin not."He said that because I don't have much of a filter sometimes when people tick me off and I just go, and that's the way he said, "Be angry and sin not."It's okay to be angry, but don't sin in your anger.

00:11:32.160 --> 00:11:41.580
Does that make sense what I'm telling y'all? So that's the lesson I've been learning in the last 48 hours: Be angry, sin not, walk in love.

00:11:41.581 --> 00:11:50.121
You must learn to walk in love; it's the only way to the greater glory. Remember the angel.

00:11:50.122 --> 00:11:56.078
He says it's always those life lessons; that's how we're going to walk with him.

00:11:56.079 --> 00:12:04.559
Even whenever people talk trash about you or run you down, your job is always to stay on the love side.

00:12:04.560 --> 00:12:10.559
Remember that because you're going to be tested just like Brandon is tested.

00:12:10.560 --> 00:12:17.956
But hopefully, you can learn from our mistakes. So be very careful who you let in your inner courts.

00:12:17.957 --> 00:12:24.347
Be careful who you let in your inner tent. Be careful who's influencing you.

00:12:24.348 --> 00:12:31.679
Watch who's speaking into your life. Watch where you're feeding.

00:12:31.680 --> 00:12:39.237
Make sure you're growing and you're going from glory to glory. It's your responsibility to monitor your thermostat.

00:12:39.238 --> 00:12:49.112
If your thermostat is cold, check your thermostat spiritually. You say, "I'm going to a church that doesn't feed me.

00:12:49.113 --> 00:12:53.243
I'm hanging around people who pull me down."Check your thermostat.

00:12:53.244 --> 00:12:58.317
There are many of you that say, "Well, I'm married into an unequally yoked marriage, Brandon.

00:12:58.318 --> 00:13:04.559
What should I do?"Well, you shouldn't have done that in the first place, but now that you're in it, you don't get a divorce.

00:13:04.560 --> 00:13:11.518
You're in covenant. So you walk it out in love and you pray for your spouse.

00:13:11.519 --> 00:13:17.400
The Bible says, "Don't be unequally yoked with unbelievers."It's your choice.

00:13:17.401 --> 00:13:23.937
Now, if you got saved during that marriage, you keep interceding. You fast, you pray, you anoint.

00:13:23.938 --> 00:13:32.799
I would take olive oil—this is what I got from Billy Burke—and I'm telling you what, solid people, Billy Burke.

00:13:32.800 --> 00:13:38.611
You anoint their pillow with oil. You anoint them at night, and they don't even have to know you're doing it.

00:13:38.611 --> 00:13:42.850
Maybe they wake up in the morning; you put a little bit on that pillow and you anoint it.

00:13:42.851 --> 00:13:51.518
And I pray over them over and over and over again. Make your prayer petition for 2026. That's what I tried to teach you all last night.

00:13:51.519 --> 00:13:59.215
We always write the vision down of everything we're believing for every single year. Whether it's a house, we write it down.

00:13:59.216 --> 00:14:06.719
It may be something so big that you know that God is the only one that can bring it to pass. And you go, "How is that even possible?

00:14:06.720 --> 00:14:16.078
This is not possible by man's standard, but it's possible through God."So you have to write your vision down.

00:14:16.079 --> 00:14:23.175
Put it down before you. Put your love scriptures, put whatever you've got. Write the vision down.

00:14:23.176 --> 00:14:33.298
Make sure you keep that in priority and put it on a mirror, on your car visor, or by your bed where you sleep on your nightstand.

00:14:33.299 --> 00:14:40.949
Make sure you have that as something that's always in front of your face. You have to keep the vision in front of you.

00:14:40.950 --> 00:14:50.719
That's why I try to tell people all the time: if you don't have big house mentality, go drive in the big neighborhoods and get that inside of you so that you can start thinking bigger.

00:14:50.720 --> 00:14:55.393
Poverty thinks poverty; rich thinks rich. Does that make sense?

00:14:55.394 --> 00:15:03.334
If you think like a winner, you don't go around a losing baseball team or a losing football team and get winning inside of you.

00:15:03.335 --> 00:15:06.829
If they're always losing, loser is going to be inside of you.

00:15:06.830 --> 00:15:10.595
You've got to get around a winner. Go watch somebody who's a champion.

00:15:10.596 --> 00:15:18.365
You've got to get that inside of you so that it changes you from the inside out. Add the Word to it, but get a vision.

00:15:18.366 --> 00:15:24.665
Get an inward vision of who you are in Christ and know that God's created you to be more than a conqueror.

00:15:24.666 --> 00:15:35.062
You are not made to be a 'just barely getting by'person. And maybe you're almost at the championship game and then you lose.

00:15:35.063 --> 00:15:40.307
Well, you learn from the losing and you get better the next year.

00:15:40.308 --> 00:15:45.608
There is a place in God that the devil does not go when you're underneath that umbrella of the anointing.

00:15:45.609 --> 00:15:52.761
You must learn to abide in love and abide in the glory of the Lord, even whenever your flesh does not want to.

00:15:52.762 --> 00:16:01.678
There are days whenever I just go, "Oh!"Like I said, I want to pull my hair out, and it's already pulled out.

00:16:01.679 --> 00:16:07.119
I'm trying to tell you all it's something Brandon's walking through, too.

00:16:07.120 --> 00:16:19.198
But I so want that when I get on the other side, I say, "Jesus, I did everything I could.

00:16:19.199 --> 00:16:28.239
I sure tried."I don't want to say, "Well, I didn't leave it all on the table.

00:16:28.240 --> 00:16:44.747
I wasn't all in."I think a lot of people might have regrets, ladies and gentlemen, but it's what you do with the time and the effort that you've been given. I came across a guy that was really ripped.

00:16:44.748 --> 00:16:59.865
He had muscles on muscles, and it challenges you because you look at him and go, "Wow, he has the same hours in a day as I have, but he's really trim and fit and he looks good, and then here I am."But where are you spiritually?

00:16:59.866 --> 00:17:07.759
I try to mirror myself off of Jesus, but at the same time, I'm going, "Where are people spiritually?"Where are people physically?

00:17:07.760 --> 00:17:16.958
I know I need to do better with my flesh, but I'm not satisfied with where I am spiritually either.

00:17:16.959 --> 00:17:27.038
I want more. I want to stand with Him. And the only way you're going to do that is to act like Jesus and be more like Him.

00:17:27.039 --> 00:17:39.519
And what did Jesus do, even whenever they were spitting on Him? Sometimes the best answer is no answer at all.

00:17:39.520 --> 00:17:51.038
Sometimes walking in love—whenever people are wanting a comment from you, wanting you to respond—sometimes to walk in love is not to give an answer at all.

00:17:51.039 --> 00:17:56.306
Just be still. Jesus didn't respond to it; He got quiet before them.

00:17:56.307 --> 00:17:59.888
They are the accusers of the brethren, the accusers of the palace.

00:17:59.889 --> 00:18:06.486
'Hey, what do you say to this?'Silence. 'They're accusing you.

00:18:06.487 --> 00:18:17.439
They want to put you to death.'Silence. So, His example is that not everything requires a reaction.

00:18:17.440 --> 00:18:31.021
I'm learning that too. Sometimes no words is a good thing. We're all a work in progress. We're all learning.

00:18:31.022 --> 00:18:37.425
But I want to teach you all as much as what I'm learning, especially today and yesterday.

00:18:37.426 --> 00:18:44.508
Walk in love. Walk in love. Love never fails. You either have it or you don't.

00:18:44.509 --> 00:18:57.119
Either you're a believing believer or you're not. That was 17 minutes—that's not too bad for that part.

00:18:57.120 --> 00:19:12.971
I could have probably said more, but I try to save your time. And even reading Diana—she's a firecracker, too. But I tell you, listening...

00:19:12.972 --> 00:19:24.860
because the Lord told us, because we're talking about pride and Leviathan and the pride behind it and the spirits that try to be sneaky and you think you're humble.

00:19:24.861 --> 00:19:32.274
But you know what? This is something else. People say, 'Braden, you're humble.''Boy, you're humble, Brandon.'People say that all the time.

00:19:32.274 --> 00:19:35.554
Either you are or you're not. There's no pretending with humility.

00:19:35.555 --> 00:19:46.090
It's displayed by a reaction of love when you realize that it's not you doing something.

00:19:46.091 --> 00:19:52.371
You don't have to convince yourself. Either you are or you're not.

00:19:52.372 --> 00:19:59.359
I don't have to walk around and try to display humility. Either it is or it's not.

00:19:59.360 --> 00:20:01.594
'Well, Brandon, you're humble. Brandon, you're prideful.

00:20:01.595 --> 00:20:11.918
Brandon, this whatever.'Either you are or you're not. You cannot fake humility.

00:20:11.919 --> 00:20:17.673
Either it's you, either it's Jesus Christ in you, or it's not. But I don't have to vocalize it.

00:20:17.674 --> 00:20:24.046
That's why I don't ever say I try to be whatever, because I know.

00:20:24.047 --> 00:20:29.839
If you look at my resume, you know Brandon doesn't have what it takes in the natural.

00:20:29.840 --> 00:20:36.918
Do you understand? Brandon is solely dependent upon Jesus. I don't have much education.

00:20:36.919 --> 00:20:41.590
People say, 'Brandon, don't knock yourself.'No, I'm stating a fact.

00:20:41.591 --> 00:20:44.572
That's not me trying to be humble; that's just stating a fact.

00:20:44.573 --> 00:20:54.387
I am flat-out nothing without Jesus Christ or my education. When you can barely read and write...

00:20:54.388 --> 00:21:01.811
things that I do read well, I've read probably a thousand times or I've studied it.

00:21:01.812 --> 00:21:10.285
If it's raw, like reading those articles that Braden puts up, you can take it to the bank: I'm going to be embarrassed. But I learned...

00:21:10.286 --> 00:21:20.232
even whenever I played games at Christmas time with people at youth parties, I would be the one hiding in the back because I was so embarrassed to play those games because they had to read and I couldn't read.

00:21:20.233 --> 00:21:25.554
I remember sitting in there and they would play those games at Christmas time and they said, 'Braden, do you want to play?'I said, 'Oh, no.

00:21:25.555 --> 00:21:30.971
I'm not interested,'and I'd make up an excuse. But really, the bottom line is I wanted to play with all my heart.

00:21:30.972 --> 00:21:41.246
I wanted to play with all my heart, but I was so ashamed that I was a teenager and I couldn't read that I didn't want to embarrass myself in front of all the high school kids.

00:21:41.247 --> 00:21:57.310
So, I would go and do something else and talk to the adults. A lot of times I'd go in and talk the Word to the mother of the party or the father because I was so ashamed that I couldn't do what the other kids were doing.

00:21:57.311 --> 00:22:04.235
That's what I developed; it was a defense mechanism. A lot of that came out of just a lot of pain.

00:22:04.236 --> 00:22:10.818
And even whenever I was a janitor and cleaning for all these years, it was the mechanism of rejection.

00:22:10.819 --> 00:22:18.228
There was so much rejection going through a lot of pastors. You know, it's like with us—nobody really cares truly about you.

00:22:18.229 --> 00:22:26.691
If I were still the janitor, nobody would give a crap. But because I have a million people following me now, people try to reach out to you.

00:22:26.692 --> 00:22:30.294
But really, the bottom line is, if you were still the janitor, they wouldn't even look your direction.

00:22:30.295 --> 00:22:35.935
They don't give a crap about you. Remember that. It's about Jesus inside of you.

00:22:35.936 --> 00:22:42.578
And when He exalts you and promotes you, people look your way. I was the janitor all the time.

00:22:42.579 --> 00:22:46.479
I went there and I cleaned 90 toilets two or three times a week.

00:22:46.480 --> 00:22:49.059
And even then, they said, 'Go in there and clean your bathrooms.

00:22:49.060 --> 00:22:54.959
You aren't going to touch nobody and lay hands on anybody.'But the glory was on my hands even then.

00:22:54.960 --> 00:22:59.445
And I could lay hands on people and the power of God would hit them and cancer would fall off their face.

00:22:59.446 --> 00:23:04.558
I'll never forget this lady walked up to me while I was vacuuming the floor.

00:23:04.559 --> 00:23:14.379
Her boy was diagnosed with stage four cancer and she came up to me while I was cleaning the church and she said, 'I've heard...

00:23:14.380 --> 00:23:20.821
we're desperate. There's nobody in this church that knows how to pray for anybody, but could you please pray for my son?

00:23:20.822 --> 00:23:30.235
He starts chemo in a couple of days. Can you lay hands on him? Do you see this knot on the side of his face?

00:23:30.236 --> 00:23:42.602
It's the size of an egg. Can you pray for it?'I said, 'Yes.'So, I shut the door because I didn't want to get in trouble.

00:23:42.603 --> 00:23:55.579
I opened the door and I said, 'Come on in here, buddy.'I said, 'In the name of Jesus Christ, I cursed that cancer and told it to go.'Three days later, she came back to the church crying.

00:23:55.580 --> 00:24:06.959
She said, 'Brandon, look, it's gone.'Not by what Brandon did, but by what Jesus did through Brandon.

00:24:06.960 --> 00:24:17.439
And when you realize 'Christ in me, Christ in me,'that little boy's life—he didn't have to go to chemo. They went back to the doctor.

00:24:17.440 --> 00:24:27.119
They went back to the doctor and the doctor said, 'What happened?'She told him and he tried to make up an excuse that it wasn't cancer.

00:24:27.120 --> 00:24:36.566
I thought it was funny. I said, 'Isn't Jesus wonderful?'Do you understand? Jesus will meet you where you are and He loves you.

00:24:36.567 --> 00:24:47.325
But when you're going through the valley with all this pressure, like I'm learning, you're not important until you have a following in the world's eyes.

00:24:47.326 --> 00:24:52.925
But Jesus saw you as important when you were scrubbing poop. Do you understand?

00:24:52.926 --> 00:25:03.288
And so I don't get into all of the political stuff even when I'm invited to the White House. It's all a show pony.

00:25:03.289 --> 00:25:13.012
I refuse to be show ponies because you weren't there when I was a janitor and you didn't care then.

00:25:13.013 --> 00:25:19.012
So I realize the bigger the platform, the bigger the call what God has put inside of me.

00:25:19.013 --> 00:25:28.843
And regardless of how much God promotes Brandon Biggs, He always says, 'Stay the janitor, Brandon.

00:25:28.844 --> 00:25:46.659
Don't ever forget where I brought you from.'Never forget it, for you're about to enter into the second phase of your ministry and healing is going to fall out of your hands and cancer is going to dry up on a greater scale.

00:25:46.660 --> 00:25:50.234
The fire is going to drive out sickness like you wouldn't believe, son.

00:25:50.235 --> 00:25:58.189
But that's going to be the time whenever your ministry really takes off. Remember this and always keep small in your own eyes.

00:25:58.190 --> 00:26:08.672
I was out doing my yard work and He always tells me that: 'Remember to stay small in your own eyes.'And it was a flattering thing even this week.

00:26:08.673 --> 00:26:13.820
