00:26:13.821 --> 00:26:22.216
And I got to see Billy Graham—the son spoke. I got to see another man.

00:26:22.217 --> 00:26:25.585
I don't know who he was, Benny Johnson. These other people were there.

00:26:25.586 --> 00:26:30.837
