00:27:29.914 --> 00:27:37.786
If you don't understand the authority of the believer, if you don't understand who you are, you're not going to make it in the days ahead.

00:27:37.787 --> 00:27:43.963
I say this not to scare you, but to prepare you. You must understand Psalms 91.

00:27:43.964 --> 00:27:49.060
You must understand Psalms 23. You must understand the authority of the believer.

00:27:49.061 --> 00:27:54.822
I always try to talk about Sister Billy. She's been such a friend.

00:27:54.823 --> 00:28:04.018
I want you to understand you must understand the authority of the believer, and you read these little books like this and you get that authority down inside you.

00:28:04.019 --> 00:28:12.555
I didn't realize how many people have no idea about who they are in Christ and you must get this down inside of you.

00:28:12.556 --> 00:28:26.518
You must, and she would even tell you to walk in love. So always stay small as much as God promotes you.

00:28:26.519 --> 00:28:32.031
And there'll be a lot of you that you've been the janitor just like Brandon Biggs.

00:28:32.032 --> 00:28:40.675
And you'll look back at your life and you'll pinch yourself at what God's about to do because all to Jesus we surrender.

00:28:40.676 --> 00:28:49.413
All to him I humbly give. Do you understand? Diana was clerical. I entered in all the offerings. I counted the offerings.

00:28:49.414 --> 00:29:00.635
I did it all for years, counting the offerings and entering in your tithe and offerings at the megachurch we worked at.

00:29:00.636 --> 00:29:12.639
And we learned a lot. But never turn your nose up to small beginnings.

00:29:12.640 --> 00:29:25.119
So because one day maybe they'll call you to want to go to the White House and maybe you will say no, maybe you'll say yes, but it's all about him.

00:29:25.120 --> 00:29:40.673
You know, all the conferences that I've been invited to to speak to tens of thousands of people on a regular basis, I'm going to say, well, it has been all of them, haven't it?

00:29:40.674 --> 00:29:48.605
All of them I have said no to. It's not funny. I just don't, I'm not into it. It's just real.

00:29:48.606 --> 00:29:54.994
And I had to say to myself, you know, well, I have to say I spoke at Sister Billy's tent thing.

00:29:54.995 --> 00:30:02.465
Yeah, and I like that. That was fun. But it wasn't on the internet, so I felt good about it. You don't have to worry about it because what if you mess up?

00:30:02.466 --> 00:30:06.929
What if you say something really stupid and it's on there and you're not in control of the video?

00:30:06.930 --> 00:30:20.849
But to me, it's just like whatever. So, all 4,040 of you, you got my little lesson today about walking in love.

00:30:20.850 --> 00:30:26.083
I was going to bring in Diana. So, if she wants to pray with us, I told her I'll talk for a second.

00:30:26.084 --> 00:30:31.075
