00:30:47.638 --> 00:30:56.394
Diana does the emails and talking to the people and getting all that done, sending out the Bibles, and then Brandon tries to keep himself full and talking to you all.

00:30:56.395 --> 00:31:15.678
And so it's pretty crazy, but all right. Hold on. Who I was going to ask this question, I don't know if you all, I tried to do this poll.

00:31:15.679 --> 00:31:19.756
A lot of these people don't know who Kathryn Kuhlman is. So I did a poll last time.

00:31:19.757 --> 00:31:24.917
I think like 30% didn't know who she was, which is amazing to me.

00:31:24.918 --> 00:31:35.932
I think it was like 30 to 40%. So, it was pretty high. Hi. She probably is cooking right now.

00:31:35.933 --> 00:32:00.798
I don't know. Here, let me see. I was going to say, do you know who Billy Graham was?

00:32:00.799 --> 00:32:06.273
Because I know a lot of people who don't know. I don't know how you couldn't know.

00:32:06.274 --> 00:32:25.357
