00:32:29.665 --> 00:32:36.933
They enjoy the Christmas lights. I don't know. I hope so. You know, we don't do that very often, but it's something fun.

00:32:36.934 --> 00:32:42.558
You want to take communion with me? Mhm. You can pray with me.

00:32:42.559 --> 00:32:48.310
Jesus, we sure love you, and we thank you, Father, for the days ahead.

00:32:48.311 --> 00:32:54.373
No matter how hard it is or how easy it is, we always give Jesus the glory.

00:32:54.374 --> 00:33:03.439
And we always keep him first. It's not always easy, but your flesh wants to be rebellious.

00:33:03.440 --> 00:33:11.318
