00:34:29.929 --> 00:34:38.059
And so it's really something I'd have to really pray about because Diana and I talked about it last night and we would do it if he asked us to.

00:34:38.060 --> 00:34:47.598
Yeah, it's been on my heart because I like to pray live. It's amazing because there's a bigger pool, you know, whenever you're with a group of people and you can feel them.

00:34:47.599 --> 00:35:01.722
But it's putting yourself out there that you have security already and making sure they're armed and that there's no more incidences like Charlie Kirk, you know, and I don't want anybody to be in harm's way because of me and having a meeting.

00:35:01.723 --> 00:35:12.190
So, I would have to hire police officers or security. So, there's a lot more to us opening a building and having something in Tulsa.

00:35:12.191 --> 00:35:21.999
I would put it by ORU because of the college kids. I have a hunger. And so, there's just things that I have to pray about a lot.

00:35:22.000 --> 00:35:30.519
And security and being safe is a major deal for us, you know, because we have a lot of people that just don't like Brandon and Diana.

00:35:30.520 --> 00:35:34.396
And that's fine. But, Father, we thank you, Lord. We thank you, Lord.

00:35:34.397 --> 00:35:39.410
I had to say that as we're praying over that. And I, Father, I thank you, Lord, for your body.

00:35:39.411 --> 00:35:43.658
We thank you, Lord, for how much you love us and how much you've taken care of us.

00:35:43.659 --> 00:35:49.508
The blood of Jesus Christ covers us. We take this body in the name of Jesus.

00:35:49.509 --> 00:35:55.153
We thank you, Lord, that by your stripes, we're healed. You were wounded for our transgressions.

00:35:55.155 --> 00:36:01.603
You were bruised for our iniquities. The chastisement of our peace was upon you, and with your stripes, we are healed.

00:36:01.604 --> 00:36:10.678
Lord, Diana and I are walking in divine health. We're not beggars; we're believers. We believe we're overcomers.

00:36:10.679 --> 00:36:20.925
We believe, Father, that everyone watching right now is healed, whole, and well by the stripes of Jesus.

00:36:20.926 --> 00:36:27.064
You walk in divine health like the little boy we prayed for who had cancer and was completely healed.

00:36:27.065 --> 00:36:35.070
We believe, Father, that you're no respecter of persons, and what you do for him, you'll do for them.

00:36:35.071 --> 00:36:40.893
Tonight, we believe that their expiration date for what they're believing for is today.

00:36:40.894 --> 00:36:45.679
Today they're overcomers. Today they're healed. Today they're whole.

00:36:45.680 --> 00:36:50.794
Today they're well. Father, they walk in divine healing and health.

00:36:50.795 --> 00:36:57.679
We thank you, Lord, for the body that was broken for us, and we take it in the mighty name of Jesus.

00:36:57.680 --> 00:37:11.559
Amen. Lord, we thank you for the blood. We make much of the blood, and the blood makes much of us.

00:37:11.560 --> 00:37:26.768
We apply the blood of Jesus from the top of our heads to the soles of our feet, so that we always stay in the right way, at the right place, at the right time.

00:37:26.769 --> 00:37:31.963
We're always in the right place at the right time doing exactly what you called us to do.

00:37:31.964 --> 00:37:35.326
We're never caught off guard. If you say don't go, we don't go.

00:37:35.327 --> 00:37:46.427
If you say go, we go. We flow with love. Father, we ooze love; that's who we are.

00:37:46.428 --> 00:37:53.547
We're just like Jesus. Regardless, we walk in love and we plead the blood over sin.

00:37:53.548 --> 00:38:04.344
We close doors that we've opened and plead the blood over those doors. We ask for mercy. Lord, have mercy on us.

00:38:04.345 --> 00:38:15.752
I thank you, Lord, regardless of whatever it is in our lives, we confess our sins, and you said you are faithful and just to forgive us and cleanse us from all unrighteousness.

00:38:15.753 --> 00:38:20.301
I plead the blood over Diana from the top of her head to the soles of her feet.

00:38:20.302 --> 00:38:23.274
We thank you, Lord, for whom the Son has set free is free indeed.

00:38:23.275 --> 00:38:28.266
We're blessed in the city and in the field, coming in and going out in the name of Jesus. Father, we plead the blood.

00:38:28.267 --> 00:38:35.289
I thank you that we are uninterrupted and unhindered by any satanic or demonic force.

00:38:35.290 --> 00:38:42.074
Father, I thank you that you speak through my vocal cords and think through my mind—all of you and none of me.

00:38:42.075 --> 00:38:52.394
Father, I plead the blood over my spiritual eyes. If there's anything you want to show us tonight in prayer, we come boldly into your throne room.

00:38:52.395 --> 00:39:05.954
I thank you, Lord, that you show us that which is to come. We have eyes to see and ears to hear, for we will hear your voice and a stranger's voice we will not follow.

00:39:05.955 --> 00:39:19.838
We will hear and see clearly, and we will not be snared by any satanic or demonic force. In Jesus'name, amen.

