That was different tonight, but I had to do something different because I felt something.

00:39:22.877 --> 00:39:34.256
What are you going to say? You okay? You touched it. Yeah, I saw that.

00:39:34.258 --> 00:39:44.167
It dumped out. You can dump some of that on your hand. I'm okay.

