00:40:06.188 --> 00:40:16.295
We thank you, Lord, for how good you have been to us. You've been good to Brandon Biggs, to my wife, and to my kids.

00:40:16.296 --> 00:40:36.078
We're so thankful for all you've done. We apply the blood of Jesus and we make much of it.

00:40:36.079 --> 00:40:42.849
Father, it never loses its power. It reaches to the highest mountain and flows to the lowest valley.

00:40:42.850 --> 00:41:13.792
