00:41:33.677 --> 00:41:53.838
It reaches to the highest mountain and flows to the lowest valley.

00:41:53.839 --> 00:42:13.519
The blood that Jesus shed for me way back on Calvary, the blood that gives me strength from day to day, will never lose its power.

00:42:13.520 --> 00:43:32.719
Father, we thank you for the blood. Your blood is sufficient for me.

00:43:32.720 --> 00:43:48.719
What can wash away my sin? Nothing but the blood of Jesus. What can make me whole again?

00:43:48.720 --> 00:44:13.118
Nothing but the blood of Jesus. Precious is the flow that makes me white as snow.

00:44:13.119 --> 00:44:50.345
No other fount I know, nothing but the blood of Jesus. Thank you, Father, for the blood.

00:44:50.346 --> 00:45:05.492
Thank you that it never loses its power. We're coming up higher to the fire. We're coming up by your side.

00:45:05.493 --> 00:45:12.958
I thank you, Lord, that we're drawn by your side and we're walking with you on a day-to-day basis.

00:45:12.959 --> 00:45:26.073
The glory of the Lord rests on us. There are many of you that need to forgive people that have hurt you.

00:45:26.074 --> 00:45:34.396
Just say it: 'I forgive them.'Walk in love. I forgive so-and-so.

00:45:34.398 --> 00:45:52.899
I forgive them by faith. Love takes no account of a suffered wrong.

00:45:52.900 --> 00:45:58.272
Be quick to forgive. Don't hold a grudge; it builds a dam in your heart.

00:45:58.273 --> 00:46:10.639
Don't allow strife and evil works to build a dam in your heart. Let the love of God flow freely inside of you like a river.

00:46:10.640 --> 00:46:23.935
It doesn't mean you have to let people keep hurting you, but don't let strife and anger keep that love from walking out of you.

00:46:23.936 --> 00:46:38.732
Just release it and let it go. Does that make sense? Many of you have taken offense at people even at church, at work, or at school.

00:46:38.733 --> 00:46:44.793
You've let them build a stronghold of bitterness inside of you.

00:46:44.794 --> 00:46:52.522
Tonight, the Lord wants you to let it go. Let the Holy Ghost flow.

00:46:52.523 --> 00:47:03.039
When you keep anger and bitterness inside of you, it brings a dam.

00:47:03.040 --> 00:47:13.303
Out of your belly shall flow rivers of living water. Love never fails.

00:47:13.304 --> 00:47:22.714
I have to talk to myself like this all the time. Shut up, flesh!

00:47:22.715 --> 00:47:41.882
Love never fails. I am rooted and grounded in love. Thank you, Father, for the Holy Ghost, for he will help you.

00:47:41.883 --> 00:47:47.071
They did me wrong with finances or a business deal. They ripped me off.

00:47:47.072 --> 00:47:50.381
They did this. They did that. You keep holding on to grudges.

00:47:50.382 --> 00:47:56.479
Well, she was a bad wife in my first marriage, boy, and I tell you what, I hope she burns and rots in hell.

00:47:56.480 --> 00:48:01.323
I mean, seriously, right? And so you build that up inside and you've got that bitterness.

00:48:01.324 --> 00:48:10.650
