I don't know if that ministers to anybody, but it's just in my spirit, I guess, because it's on the topic.

00:50:46.720 --> 00:50:53.395
Don't take it into your next marriage. Especially, I see a woman—I just saw a vision right then.

00:50:53.396 --> 00:51:04.118
And I see the woman: You're getting ready to get married. It's going to be a new transition in your life come January of 2026 around this time frame.

