This is rewinding in slow motion in front of my eyes right now. And I see it all moving back and you are so, so bitter still.

00:51:46.319 --> 00:51:54.799
And the Lord tells me this next marriage won't last very long if you don't bring it to my throne.

00:51:54.800 --> 00:52:18.799
You must bring this to my throne or the next marriage won't last very long.

