00:53:36.157 --> 00:54:00.799
He wants to turn the sorrow, the grieving, the grieving. There's great grieving.

00:54:00.800 --> 00:54:25.439
Let it go. Let it go. You're even upset with how much you didn't get in the divorce.

00:54:25.440 --> 00:54:32.938
