00:54:32.939 --> 00:54:48.696
'I should have gotten more at the court. I should have gotten more at that divorce.'Harmony, you must stop this.

00:54:48.697 --> 00:54:54.434
I hear the spirit of the Lord say you must stop this. He has more.

00:54:54.435 --> 00:55:02.719
This will be the most joyous time of restoring what the cankerworm ate in your life.

00:55:02.720 --> 00:55:08.887
You will have the most joyous time if you don't take this into the next relationship.

